  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "八宝辣酱的味道",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "39980458_3_2775-2876",
          "range": "2775-2876",
          "rangeStart": 2775,
          "rangeEnd": 2876,
          "markText": "汪曾祺在家做过八宝辣酱吗？偶尔做过，味道还行，不过没盖过帽子，可能也不太懂这些规矩。老头儿虽然被称为美食家，但只是作家中的厨子，主业还是文学创作。他写的吃喝，只可咂摸其中的文学意味，依样画葫芦准得砸锅。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1717546738,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-05 08:18:58",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2775&rangeEnd=2876",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2775&rangeEnd=2876"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "39980458_3_1686-1799",
          "range": "1686-1799",
          "rangeStart": 1686,
          "rangeEnd": 1799,
          "markText": "汪曾祺的作品，有着各种味道，酸甜苦辣都沾点边儿。尽管他将自己创作的主旨概括为“人间送小温”，有意识地向读者呈现世间的美好事物，描述生活中好玩儿的一面，但是这个老头儿毕竟生活在当下，经历过不少运动，也受过一些揉搓，有着各种感受。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1717546572,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-05 08:16:12",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1686&rangeEnd=1799",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1686&rangeEnd=1799"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
