    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980458_10_9751-9781",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9751-9781",
      "markText": "安乐居已经没有了。房子翻盖过了。现在那儿是一个什么贸易中心。",
      "totalCount": 2412,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9751&rangeEnd=9781",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9751&rangeEnd=9781"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980458_6_8732-8829",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8732-8829",
      "markText": "这金昌焕真是缺德，偷了文嫂的鸡，还借了文嫂的鼎罐来炖了。至于他怎么偷的鸡，怎样宰了，怎样煺的鸡毛，谁都无从想象。 林子大了，什么鸟都有。",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8732&rangeEnd=8829",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8732&rangeEnd=8829"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980458_3_658-686",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "658-686",
      "markText": "如今有人为了健康，将猪油换成了植物油，那就没什么吃头了。",
      "totalCount": 1650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=658&rangeEnd=686",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=658&rangeEnd=686"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980458_20_4069-4118",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4069-4118",
      "markText": "薛大娘身心都很健康。她的性格没有被扭曲、被压抑。舒舒展展，无拘无束。这是一个彻底解放的，自由的人。",
      "totalCount": 1536,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980458&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4069&rangeEnd=4118",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/83b321d072620daa83bd893?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4069&rangeEnd=4118"
    },
